<i class="ri-ancient-gate-line ri-2x text-primary"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Ancient Traditions</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">Preserving liturgical practices and religious traditions that date back to the early Christian church.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
<div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
<i class="ri-book-2-line ri-2x text-primary"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Sacred Texts</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">Maintaining unique biblical canons including the Book of Enoch and other ancient manuscripts.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
