<i class="ri-building-line ri-2x text-primary"></i>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Church Heritage</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">Home to remarkable architectural wonders like the churches of Lalibela, carved from solid rock.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-white/80 rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 mb-16">
