<p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">The Ethiopian Orthodox Church has played a crucial role in preserving Ethiopia's cultural and literary heritage. The church has maintained ancient manuscripts, art, and musical traditions that continue to influence Ethiopian culture today.</p>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-center">
